[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **FUNCTION CALL ALTERNATIVES:**                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```javascript                                                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m alert(1)                      → alert`1`                                     [34m│[0m
