[34m│[0m - `onmouseover`, `onmouseenter`                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - `onkeydown`, `onkeypress`, `onkeyup`                                       [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - `onpointerover`, `onpointerdown`, `onpointerenter`                         [34m│[0m
